headline: Seagate Note Exchange Reshapes Debt Mix As Valuation Signals Upside Potential
summary: Seagate Technology Holdings (NasdaqGS:STX) has completed previously disclosed exchange agreements for its Exchangeable Senior Notes. The company exchanged $600 million principal amount of these notes for a mix of cash and Seagate shares. This transaction represents a capital structure adjustment focused on balance sheet management.
